title: Britney Spears - Perfume [Single]
description:
"Perfume" is a song recorded by American singer Britney Spears for her forthcoming eighth studio album, Britney Jean (2013). It was written by Spears, Chris Braide and Sia Furler and produced by will.i.am, Braide and Keith Harris. A musical departure from its EDM-influenced predecessor, "Work Bitch", the song was met with positive reception from fans and critics.

Released: November 4, 2013
Recorded: 2013
Length: 4:00
Label: RCA
Writer(s): Britney Spears, Chris Braide, Sia Furler
Producer: will.i.am, Chris Braide, Keith Harris
